{
  "stem": "15115.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Strictly-- it doesn't make sense, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- it wasn't hatred.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not teaching hatred.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was-- but they were teaching discipline more than hatred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was no-- [PAUSES FOR 2 SECONDS] you could say there might have been a little bit of an anti-Semite [INAUDIBLE] in Greece, in Salonika.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But you don't-- you didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you walk on the street, you didn't care if you were a Jew or a gentile.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody will say you're a dirty Jew or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We didn't have that when I was growing up, anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't mean anything to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was only, what? 12 years old, 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What-- what did I know at the time?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the meantime, I belonged to the Boy Scouts, the Jewish Boy Scouts, in the same time, because you're used to having a different group.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it didn't mean anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We used to go parade with the Jewish scouts, the Jew-- I used to have the uniform and everything else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But doesn't-- it didn't mean very much, because we never thought in my age-- never thought too much of-- of the Semites and everything like that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- first of all, I was mixed up with gentile friends and I was mixed up with Jewish friends, and I didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't-- it might have been a little bit of anti-Semite [? culture, ?] you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And ?] every country is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But not to the extent from what I hear today from my friends in-- in Toronto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The friends that I do have.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't have no Greek friends, only a Polish and Hungarians, and Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we get together.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
